’Щ@93275077c98ab7edf1648f3430a2fe8ae622c132950b296579ec51ecf5a665a9ЪLTitle: title: bytes collect
Path: Examples
Content:
Create a byte array from input.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [0x[11] 0x[13 15]] | bytes collect
Length: 3 (0x3) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   11 13 15                                             вЂўвЂўвЂў


```
Create a byte array from input with a separator.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [0x[11] 0x[33] 0x[44]] | bytes collect 0x[01]
Length: 5 (0x5) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   11 01 33 01  44                                      вЂўвЂў3вЂўD


```
